00:00:14.160 --> 00:00:22.360
THE 
BOEING 787.

00:00:22.360 --> 00:00:23.360
SOLD AS A "DREAMLINER".

00:00:23.360 --> 00:00:34.430
Jim McNerney: A once in a decade if not once
in a generation achievement of human ingenuity.

00:00:34.430 --> 00:00:37.980
FOR AIRLINES IT'S CHEAP TO FLY.

00:00:37.980 --> 00:00:41.830
FOR PASSENGERS IT OFFERS UNPARALLELED
