00:00:46.329 --> 00:00:50.270
PRESIDENT OBAMA: The Dreamliner is the plane
of the future.

00:00:50.270 --> 00:00:53.210
BUT AL JAZEERA DISCOVERS A DARK SIDE TO THE
DREAMLINER:

00:00:53.210 --> 00:00:59.309
STAN SORSCHER: unimaginable that we could
be three years late, have a fleet grounding,

00:00:59.309 --> 00:01:04.280
have fires on the airplane.

00:01:04.280 --> 00:01:08.130
OUR INVESTIGATION FINDS BOEING ALTERED ITS
